    "Id": "chassisdef_tora_TRA-2",
    "Name": "Tora",
    "Details": "The Tora 2 was developed after a single year of feedback from Spirit Cat MechWarriors. By removing the original's main weaponry and jump jets—but retaining the Supercharger and Targeting Computer—designers were able to install a Class 20 Hyper Assault Gauss Rifle and twin Improved Heavy Large Lasers. While the design presents potential heat issues, any experienced MechWarrior can effectively manage the heat buildup.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Easy to Pilot</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.13</color></b>\n\n<color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limits: Left Lower, Right Lower</color>\n\n<b><color=#0064e6>Used with permission from Aries Games and Miniatures.</color></b>",
