  "StockRole": "Skirmisher",
  "YangsThoughts": "The Spirit Cats urgently needed to replace their aging Cauldron-Born \"Ebon Jaguar\" OmniMechs but couldn’t produce a new design themselves due to recent turmoil and losses. They turned to the Sea Fox Spina Khanate for help, who completed the designs and passed them to Adam Tech Industries for manufacturing. The resulting Tora - a well-rounded, standard mech - is not a direct replacement but offers solid speed, mobility, and firepower. Based on the Cave Lion design for ease of manufacture, the Tora features 150-meter jump jets and a supercharger enabling bursts up to 103 kph.",
